title: Number of all operations in a slapd instance
agents: linux
catalog: app/slapd
license: GPL
distribution: Markus Weber
description:
 This check monitors all Operation types, you can set warn and crit
 thresholds to each type. There is also a deviance check wich alarms you about
 the ratio of Initiated to Completed operations

item:
 SLAPD {{Instance name}} Operations

perfdata:
 one for each operation type.

inventory:
 One service will be created for each slapd instance configured in local config file.
